{"tid":1439225,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝備]香城Online安全帽改裝","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:10:53.000Z","uid":158424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa69543bba3c3ed16de253f5d6e3ad77107e9c1","tid":1439225,"uid":158424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"夏日炎炎嘅星期六日又係工友開工嘅時候<br />\n戴安全帽可以好好保護自己 記得無論咩人都隨身攜帶<br />\n但夏天只戴安全帽又會曬到耳仔同頸<br />\n見好多人帶安全帽開工都冇遮耳仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實只需要一塊冰巾就可以將安全帽改裝到遮到耳仔<br />\n<br />\n有部份安全帽頭箍同帽殼比較少連接 會方便安裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJzQYnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJzQYnA.jpg&h=b6bdd67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲就冇咁方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Wom42C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Wom42C.jpg&h=94766900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安裝：將冰巾從頭盔兩邊攝入去頭箍同帽殼中間 從另一邊攝返出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfRzFAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfRzFAZ.jpg&h=13cadaf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成之後 可以喺頭盔嘅後方用自己嘅方法夾起塊冰巾嘅兩邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ti6WTV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTi6WTV1.jpg&h=b03e3686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記得夾得落少少 預留多少少位置 唔好因為改裝而限制到頭箍嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以夏天帶安全帽嘅時候防曬 仲可以抹下汗<br />\n希望呢兩日開工見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050d21ed74a068fa4541aed524170a0a7e388753","tid":1439225,"uid":158424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"e3f8b80cd5dfec76aaa5ca89fc240e1a1515176f